Quote: A further (obsolescent) Maori name is <i>Niu Tireni</i>, the Maori transliteration of <i>New Zealand</i> (with many variants: <i>Niu Tirani, Niu Tirini, Nuitereni, Nui Tireni, Nu Tirani</i>, etc...Both <i>Aotearoa</i> and <i>Niu Tireni</i>.. are listed among the Maori place names approved for addressing purposes by New Zealand Post.
